how to be admin because there is no owner in 667+: go to player.java shear for timebroken change it to your server name safe compile done

how to be donator: ingame when u are admin do ;;permdonator then ur ingame name

how to change shops and npc spawns object spawn:
shops: goto data items then see unpackedshops.txt change it there
npc spawns: goto data then npc u see npcspawnslist change things there safe it then delete
the map packedspawns (it come back when u start the server)
object spawns : goto data>map> unpackedspawnlist change things there safe then delete the map packed spawns (it come back when u start the server)

then compile it and see ur work in game
